data.description: Welcome to this charming, recently renovated condo! This unique community does not feel like your traditional complex - you are surrounded by nature w/ extensive greenery & quiet neighborhood. This ideal corner lot features ground level access, fenced in private patio w/ storage & is close to parking. It does not stop there, step inside and be greeted by spacious open floor plan, statement floor to ceiling stone fireplace & kitchen boasting granite countertops, modern backsplash, and SS appliances. The newly renovated bathroom has all new fixtures & gorgeous subway tile shower. Enjoy the summer sitting poolside or reserve the onsite cabana for a private event! On-site laundry facilities. Close to local shops, dining, & easy freeway access.
